2011年，德意志交易所與紐約泛歐證券交易所進行第三次高級合併協商，如談判成功將合併成歷史上最大的交易所，<ref>{{cite news
 |url=http://business.timesonline.co.uk/tol/business/industry_sectors/banking_and_finance/article5303390.ece
 |title=Talks to create world's biggest exchange
 |work=Times Online
 |accessdate=2008-12-09
 |date=2008-12-08
 |location=London
 |first=Martin
 |last=Waller
 |archive-date=2011-06-12
 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110612084515/http://business.timesonline.co.uk/tol/business/industry_sectors/banking_and_finance/article5303390.ece
 |dead-url=no
 }}</ref>紐約泛歐證券交易所與德意志交易所的股東分別於2011年7月7日及7月15日批准該項合併案，<ref name="Kara Scannell"/><ref>{{Cite news|title=Deutsche Börse Wins 82% Backing for NYSE Deal|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB10001424052702304521304576448133230979762|newspaper=Wall Street Journal|date=2011-07-15|accessdate=2020-03-03|issn=0099-9660|language=en-US|first=Jacob|last=Bunge|archive-date=2021-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210324085236/https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB10001424052702304521304576448133230979762|dead-url=no}}</ref>於2011年12月22日獲美國證券交易委員會批准，<ref>{{Cite news|title=Deutsche Boerse, NYSE deal wins U.S. approval|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-nyse-deutscheboerse-idUSTRE7BL1CE20111222|author=Diane Bartz|newspaper=Reuters|date=2011-12-22|accessdate=2020-03-03|language=en|archive-date=2021-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210324085223/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-nyse-deutscheboerse-idUSTRE7BL1CE20111222|dead-url=no}}</ref>但[[歐盟委員會|歐盟委員會]]於2012年2月1日以新公司將導致歐洲金融市場出現壟斷為由阻止該項交易，<ref>{{Cite web|title=Press corner|url=https://ec.europa.eu/commission/presscorner/home/en|date=2012-02-01|accessdate=2020-03-03|work=European Commission|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126142239/https://ec.europa.eu/commission/presscorner/home/en|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|title=EU blocks merger of NYSE-Deutsche|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/business-16838793|newspaper=BBC News|date=2012-02-01|accessdate=2020-03-03|language=en-GB|archive-date=2021-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210324090416/https://www.bbc.com/news/business-16838793|dead-url=no}}</ref>德意志交易所對此提出上訴，最終並未成功。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Deutsche Borse To Appeal EU Veto Of NYSE Euronext|url=https://www.ibtimes.com/deutsche-borse-appeal-eu-veto-nyse-euronext-427538|accessdate=2020-03-03|date=2012-03-20|last=AM|first=Benjamin Reeves|work=International Business Times|language=en|archive-date=2021-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210324085246/https://www.ibtimes.com/deutsche-borse-appeal-eu-veto-nyse-euronext-427538|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|title=EU Rejects Deutsche Börse Appeal Against Blocked Merger With NYSE-Euronext|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/eu-rejects-deutsche-borse-appeal-against-blocked-merger-with-nyse-euronext-1425893554|newspaper=Wall Street Journal|date=2015-03-09|accessdate=2020-03-03|issn=0099-9660|language=en-US|first=Tom|last=Fairless|archive-date=2021-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210324085302/https://www.wsj.com/articles/eu-rejects-deutsche-borse-appeal-against-blocked-merger-with-nyse-euronext-1425893554|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2012年，泛歐交易所宣佈設立倫敦泛歐交易所，在英國本地提供上市服務。並於2014年6月成為英國{{le|金融服务监管局|Financial Conduct Authority}}認可的投資交易所（RIE）。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Euronext UK secures RIE status|url=http://www.ftseglobalmarkets.com/news/euronext-uk-secures-rie-status.html|accessdate=2020-03-03|author=|date=2014-06-04|format=|publisher=FTSE Global Markets|language=en|archive-date=2020-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200331175015/http://www.ftseglobalmarkets.com/news/euronext-uk-secures-rie-status.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

===洲際交易所集團收購===
2012年12月，[[洲際交易所集團|洲際交易所集團]]宣布計畫以82億美元收購紐約泛歐證券交易所，<ref>{{Cite news|title=ICE to buy NYSE Euronext for $8.2 billion|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-ice-nyse-idUSBRE8BJ0LK20121220|author1=John McCrank|author2=Luke Jeffs|newspaper=Reuters|date=2012-12-20|accessdate=2020-03-03|language=en|archive-date=2021-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210324085300/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-ice-nyse-idUSBRE8BJ0LK20121220|dead-url=no}}</ref>該計畫於2013年6月3日獲得紐約泛歐證券交易所和洲際交易所集團的股東同意，<ref>{{Cite web|title=NYSE Euronext Shareholders Approve ICE Merger|url=https://www.cnbc.com/id/100784899|accessdate=2020-03-03|date=2013-06-03|last=Pisani|first=Bob|work=CNBC|language=en|archive-date=2021-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210324090642/https://www.cnbc.com/id/100784899|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite press release
