===重新獨立上市===
2014年6月20日，泛歐交易所透過首次公開募股脫離洲際交易所集團，<ref>{{Cite web|title=Euronext Detaches From ICE Through $1.2 Billion IPO|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/2014-06-19/ice-may-price-euronext-near-lower-end-in-1-1-billion-ipo.html|accessdate=2020-03-03|author1=Ruth David|author2=Elco van Groningen|author3=Francesca Cinelli|date=2014-06-20|first=|format=|publisher=Bloomberg|language=en-US|archive-date=2014-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141021200510/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2014-06-19/ice-may-price-euronext-near-lower-end-in-1-1-billion-ipo.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>1​​1家公司組成財團開始對該公司投資以穩定泛歐交易所，該財團持股33.36％，且擁有3年的{{le|閉鎖期|Lock-up period}}。<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.ft.com/intl/cms/s/0/55cc0702-e573-11e3-8b90-00144feabdc0.html?siteedition=intl#axzz3GDlcZQje|title = ICE to sell third of Euronext to institutions in pan-European IPO|date = 2014-05-27|accessdate = 2014-10-15|website = Financial Times|publisher = |last = |first = }}</ref>

2019年6月18日，泛歐交易所以68億[[挪威克朗|挪威克朗]]成功收購[[奧斯陸證券交易所|奧斯陸證券交易所]]。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Acquisition of Oslo Børs VPS|url=https://euronext.com/en/investor-relations/financial-calendar/acquisition-oslo-bors-vps|date=|accessdate=2020-03-03|work=Euronext|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210202164614/https://www.euronext.com/en/investor-relations/financial-calendar/acquisition-oslo-bors-vps|dead-url=no}}</ref>2019年12月5日，宣布將收購歐洲第二大電力供應商{{le|Nord Pool|Nord Pool}} 66％的股份，並於於2019年1月15日完成收購。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Euronext completes acquisition of Nord Pool|url=https://www.nordpoolgroup.com/message-center-container/newsroom/exchange-message-list/2020/q1/euronext-completes-the-acquisition-of-nord-pool/|date=2020-01-15|accessdate=2020-03-03|work=Nord Pool|archive-date=2021-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210324090702/https://www.nordpoolgroup.com/message-center-container/newsroom/exchange-message-list/2020/q1/euronext-completes-the-acquisition-of-nord-pool/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Euronext completes the acquisition of Nord Pool|url=http://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2020/01/15/1971025/0/en/Euronext-completes-the-acquisition-of-Nord-Pool.html|accessdate=2020-03-03|date=2020-01-15|work=GlobeNewswire News Room|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210324085526/http://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2020/01/15/1971025/0/en/Euronext-completes-the-acquisition-of-Nord-Pool.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>2020年4月23日，泛歐交易所宣布以1.5億歐元收購[[丹麥|丹麥]]中央證券託管機構{{tsl|da|VP Securities|VP Securities}}70％的股權<ref>{{Cite web|title=Euronext to Acquire Control of CSD Operator VP Securities|url=https://www.financemagnates.com/institutional-forex/euronext-to-acquire-control-of-csd-operator-vp-securities/|accessdate=2020-12-03|date=2020-04-23|work=Finance Magnates|last=Abdel-Qader|first=Aziz|language=en|archive-date=2021-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210324085518/https://www.financemagnates.com/institutional-forex/euronext-to-acquire-control-of-csd-operator-vp-securities/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並於同年8月4日完成交易。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Euronext completes acquisition of Danish VP Securities|url=https://www.fnlondon.com/articles/euronext-completes-acquisition-of-danish-vp-securities-20200804|date=2020-08-04|accessdate=2020-12-03|last=Sim|first=Bérengère|work=Financial News|language=en-GB|archive-date=2021-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210324085524/https://www.fnlondon.com/articles/euronext-completes-acquisition-of-danish-vp-securities-20200804|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2020年9月18日，[[倫敦證券交易所集團|倫敦證券交易所集團]]與泛歐交易所進行獨家談判，該集團將其位於[[米蘭|米蘭]]的[[義大利證券交易所|義大利證券交易所]]（倫敦證券交易所集團所控股的100％股權）以43.3億歐元出售給泛歐交易所。<ref>{{Cite web |title=Euronext以1459億元買下米蘭證券交易所 |url=https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202010090143.aspx |accessdate=2020-12-03 |author=劉淑琴 |date=2020-10-09 |publisher=中央通訊社 |language=zh-hant |editor=曾依璇 |location=Paris |archive-date=2021-03-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210324085521/https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202010090143.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>作為交易的一部分，義大利的國有存貸款公司{{tsl|en|Cassa Depositi e Prestiti|卡薩存貸款銀行}}100％持股的{{tsl|en|CDP Equity|主權財富基金 (義大利)|主權財富基金}}以及[[義大利聯合聖保羅銀行|義大利聯合聖保羅銀行]]成為泛歐交易所的股東。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/uk-lse-borsa-italiana-m-a-idUKKBN26T1IG |title=LSE expected to approve Borsa sale to Euronext on Thursday - sources |last=Valentina |first=Za |date=2020-10-08 |last2=Giselda |first2=Vagnoni |newspaper=Reuters |accessdate=2020-12-03 |location=Milan |language=en |last3=Barbaglia |first3=Pamela |last4=Nikolaeva |first4=Maya |editor=Jan Harvey |archive-date=2021-03-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210324085516/https://www.reuters.com/article/uk-lse-borsa-italiana-m-a-idUKKBN26T1IG |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=倫敦證交所確定出售義大利證交所 以1450億元賣給泛歐交易所 |url=https://finance.ettoday.net/news/1827992 |accessdate=2020-12-03 |date=2020-10-09 |publisher=ETtoday新聞雲 |language=zh-hant |archive-date=2021-03-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210324085521/https://finance.ettoday.net/news/1827992 |dead-url=no }}</ref>《[[路透社|路透社]]》報導，倫敦證券交易所集團出售義大利證交所為該集團監管補救措施的一部分，以促使歐洲聯盟批准其以270億美元收購數據公司[[路孚特|路孚特]]，[[歐盟執行委員會|歐盟執行委員會]]於同年在12月中旬正式聲明，只有在倫敦證交所集團出售義大利證交所的情況下，才可允許其收購路孚特。泛歐交易所對義大利交易所的收購預計於2021年上半年完成。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-lse-borsa-italiana-m-a-idUSKBN26U0HF |title=LSE agrees to sell Borsa Italiana to Euronext for $5 billion |last=Nikolaeva |first=Maya |date=2020-10-09 |last2=Kar-Gupta |first2=Sudip |newspaper=Reuters |accessdate=2020-12-03 |location=London, Paris |language=en |last3=Armstrong |first3=Rachel |editor1=Simon Jessop |editor2=Jason Neely |editor3=Emelia Sithole-Matarise |archive-date=2021-03-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210324085520/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-lse-borsa-italiana-m-a-idUSKBN26U0HF |dead-url=no }}</ref>

